Orzo pasta salad .. Delicious on it‚Äôs own or as part of a main meal.. I served this with roast chicken & loaded wedges  To make this salad you will need:  260g orzo pasta 1/2 cucumber diced 1/2 red & yellow bell pepper diced 1 small red onion diced  3 tubs of sun dried tomato & mozzarella pearls - I buy the pre made up packs from Asda  3-4 tbsp red pepper pesto  Fresh basil  Cracked black pepper to taste  Simply boil the orzo according to pack instructions then run under cold water to cool. Add all the chopped salad along with the sundried tomato & mozzarella, the pesto & give everything a good mix Add in some chopped basil, season to taste with the pepper & give everything a final mix Add Taste the salad and adjust if necessary to your liking with any more of any of the ingredients & serve as required  #pasta #pastasalad #lunch #lunchinspo #mealideas #lunchideas #quicklunch #salads #cleaneating #foodies #fyp
